  "commit_message": "Add AssociatedSourceType for conditional unmanaged exports (#128180)\n\nResolves #127634\n\n`UnmanagedCallersOnlyAttribute` exports with `EntryPoint` were always\nrooted and emitted. This adds an associated source type so NativeAOT can\nkeep/export generated native entrypoints only when the source type\nsurvives trimming.\n\n- **Public API**\n- Adds `UnmanagedCallersOnlyAttribute.AssociatedSourceType` to\nimplementation and ref assemblies.\n  - Leaves the lightweight Runtime.Base attribute copy unchanged.\n\n",
